<section class="mb-20">
  <div class="text-xl">
    {{heading('Curatorial work', 1)}}
    <p class="">
      My curatorial work is informed by an ongoing research about the surrounding conditions of independent artistic practices, and characterized by close collaboration with international artists in support of new productions.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-20">
  <div class="text-xl mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-gray-400">
      {{ heading('Project management', 2) }}
    </h2>
    <p class="">
      I conceive and develop sensible formats in the field of contemporary art and culture, both self-initiated as well as commissioned, and commit to their long-term establishment.
    </p>
  </div>
  <ul>
    {%- for project in projectmanagement -%}
      {{ item(project.name, project.text, project.year)}}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="mb-20">
  <div class="text-xl mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-gray-400">
      {{ heading('Production', 3) }}
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl">
      I collaborate with artists, curators, and designers on the production of artworks, books, and editions, as well as the realization of exhibitions, events, and showcases.
    </p>
  </div>
  <p>
    <ul>
      <li>Micah Schippa exhibition at Pech</li>
      <li>Screenings at Pinacoteca</li>
      <li>Pina at Salzburger Kunstverein</li>
      <li>CLOSER Book</li>
      <li>CLOSER Panel Discussion</li>
      <li>CLOSER Branding and CI</li>
      <li>CLOSER Event at Pech</li>
      <li>James Lewis exhibition at Pech</li>
      <li>Rage and Stagnation T-Shirt</li>
      <li>Pech Lighter</li>
      <li>Opening Doppler</li>
      <li>Goswell Road / Will Benedict Edition</li>
      <li>Zone 1</li>
      <li>Alison Veit</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
</section>

<section class="mb-20">
  <div class="text-xl mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-gray-400">
     {{ heading('Web development', 4) }}
    </h2>
    <p class="">
      I design and develop fully tailored websites that are useful, simple, and effortless to maintain. Currently <span class="text-green-500">available</span> for new commissions, consulting, and development services for other designers and agencies.
    </p>
  </div>
  <ul class="flex flex-col">
    {%- for item in sites -%}
      {% if item.online == false %}
        <li class="sm:grid grid-cols-8 flex-col justify-between relative py-3 border-b border-gray-400">
          <div class="col-span-2">
            <h2 class="opacity-40">{{ item.name }} (offline)</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-span-5">
            <p class="text-gray-400">{{ item.text }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-span-1 text-right">
            {{ item.year }}
          </div>
        </li>
      {% else %}
        <a class="link | group" href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" noopener noreferrer data-frame-info-top="" data-frame-info-btm="
              <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-4'>
                <span class='name text-sm'>{{ item.name }}</span>
                {% for tech in item.tech %}
                  <div class='flex gap-2 items-center'>
                    <div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full relative overflow-hidden flex text-sm'>
                      <i class='w-full h-full' data-tech='{{ tech }}'></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class='techname opacity-50 text-sm'>{{ tech }}</span>
                  </div>
                {% endfor %}
                </div>
                ">
          <li class="sm:grid grid-cols-8 flex-col justify-between relative py-3 border-y border-gray-400 -mt-px">
            <div class="col-span-2">
              <h2 class="">{{ item.name }}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 mt-2 sm:mt-0">
              <p class="text-gray-400">{{ item.text }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 text-right hidden sm:block">
            {{ item.year }}
          </div>
          </li>
        </a>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="mb-20">
  <div class="text-xl mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-gray-400">
      {{ heading('Other work', 5) }}
    </h2>
    <p class="">
      I regularly participate in talks, workshops, panels, and exchanges. I studied creative writing and fine art in Vienna, and have experience in editorial work, translation, consulting, fundraising, construction, electronics, interior design...
    </p>
  </div>
    <ul>
      <li>Bureaucracy Studies, Lausanne</li>
      <li>viennacontemporary art fair, Vienna</li>
      <li>University of Applied Arts, Vienna</li>
      <li>Youth Salon, Zagreb</li>
      <li>Stage Bregenz, Bregenz</li>
      <li>2mares, Marseille</li>
    </ul>
</section>

